{
	"name": "Avenges the Fallen",
	"type": "feature",
	"img": "icons/magic/death/skull-energy-light-white.webp",
	"system": {
		"description": "<p><em>Passive: When an allied creature you can see is reduced to 0 HP by a hostile creature, you gain advantage on attack rolls against that creature until the end of your next turn.</em></p><p><em><strong>Legend Dice Feature</strong></em><strong> — Blood Oath:</strong> When a creature damages you or an ally, you can expend a Legend Die to mark them. Until the end of this creature’s next turn, any attacks against the marked creature are made with an expertise die, and damage against it can be rerolled, but you must take the new result.</p>",
